-- Felix Resources says has takeover interest
-- 
-- Sun Jul 27, 2008 7:44pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/07/27/us-felix-approaches-idUSSYU00480920080727

 

 SYDNEY  (Reuters) - Felix Resources Ltd FLX.AX, an Australian coal miner with a A$3.5 billion ($3.3 billion) market value, said it has received takeover interest from a number of parties. 

 "At this stage the interest shown by these parties is preliminary, incomplete, non-binding and conditional. No formal written offer has been made to Felix," the company said in a statement. ($1=A$1.33) (Reporting by James Thornhill)